high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the black plate that's in front of you on the counter.
Turn right and take a step to your right then step forward once and turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take three steps then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the sink.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter, then turn right and face the right counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Step to the right and face the fridge.
Place the plate in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and veer left to the sink.
Place the plate in the sink, to the left of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate in a fridge.

high_descs: Go forward toward the sink, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Go to the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge, put the plate inside and chill it, then take the plate out.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the sink.
